<section id="To_add_a_widget" remap="TID_15428">
	<title>Adding a Widget</title>
	<para>
		You can add widgets to the dashboard to accommodate what information you want to see upon login.
	</para>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Add a Widget</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to menu:Cloud Intelligence[Dashboard].
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/2259.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> <guibutton>(Add a Widget)</guibutton>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Select the widget you want to add from the list. Note that only widgets that are not currently showing on the dashboard will appear in this list.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
</section>